Reproductive assistance for infected couples with bloodborne viruses.

Savasi V(1), Ferrazzi E, Fiore S.

Author information:
(1)Department of Obstetrics and Gynaecology, Sacco Clinical Sciences Institute, 
University of Milan Medical School, Via GB Grassi 74, 20157 Milan, Italy. 
