Pearce J(1), Tisch C, Barnett R.

Author information:
(1)GeoHealth Laboratory, Department of Geography, University of Canterbury, 
Private Bag 4800, Christchurch, New Zealand. jamie.pearce@canterbury.ac.nz

AIMS: To monitor geographical inequalities in cause-specific mortality in New 
Zealand during the period 1980 to 2001, a time of rapid social and economic 
change.
